{"lastModified":1772786727078,"uri":"c::7579706445::vessel::d5cabfd1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Greek Islands\n\nThe 64ft/19.5m Altamar 64 motor yacht Lady L was built in 2006 and she has been through an extensive refit program in 2021. M/Y Lady L offer stylish cruising for up to 8 guests with comfortable overnight accommodation in 4 staterooms. Her interior layout includes two double cabins, one twin cabin and one twin with bunk beds, all with private ensuite facilities. She is managed by a qualified crew of 2(+1 optional) willing to satisfy guests needs and wants. The exterior living areas offer a sunbathing space on the foredeck and a seating area on the fly bridge offered for an alfresco dining surrounded by marvelous scenery. From the fine modern lines of the exterior to the spacious interior in combination with her performance, Lady L is an ideal yacht for daily cruises or long weekend charters. Oriented for families or friends who would desire to explore sandy beaches, small bays and coves less reachable from larger yachts.","blueprint":{"name":"LADY L","images":["/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cabfd1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::13529a00-a36c-11ee-aa88-e577ce1d9797.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cabfd1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::1407b930-a36c-11ee-aa88-e577ce1d9797.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cabfd1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::14d82890-a36c-11ee-aa88-e577ce1d9797.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cabfd1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::15c7dfc0-a36c-11ee-aa88-e577ce1d9797.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cabfd1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::17defff0-a36c-11ee-aa88-e577ce1d9797.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7579706445::vessel::d5cabfd1-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::18c89ca0-a36c-11ee-aa8